 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# üîó M√≥dulo 7 ‚Äî Pandas: Mezclas, Joins y Concatenaciones\n",
    "\n",
    "En este notebook aprender√°s todas las t√©cnicas de combinaci√≥n de datos:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `concat` (vertical y horizontal)\n",
    "- `merge` (inner, left, right, outer)\n",
    "- Joins por columna y por √≠ndice\n",
    "- Uniones avanzadas (one-to-many)\n",
    "- `merge_asof` para series temporales\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Dataset de ejemplo"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "ventas = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'id': [1,2,3,4],\n",
    "    'producto': ['A','B','C','D'],\n",
    "    'unidades': [10,20,15,8]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "precios = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'producto': ['A','B','C','E'],\n",
    "    'precio': [100, 80, 50, 25]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "ventas, precios"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 2Ô∏è‚É£ Concatenaci√≥n (`concat`)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Vertical (una tabla debajo de otra)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "pd.concat([ventas, ventas])"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Horizontal (lado a lado)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": [],
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "pd.concat([ventas, precios], axis=1)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Merge b√°sico (tipo SQL JOIN)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Inner Join (solo coincidencias)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='inner')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Left Join (mantiene las ventas, a√±ade precio donde pueda)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='left')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Right Join (mantiene los precios)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='right')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Outer Join (todo con todo)"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='outer')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Merge con diferentes nombres de columnas\n",
    "\n",
    "Ejemplo: columna `producto` en una tabla y `item` en otra."
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "precios_alt = precios.rename(columns={'producto':'item'})\n",
    "ventas.merge(precios_alt, left_on='producto', right_on='item', how='left')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Merge por √≠ndice\n"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ventas_idx = ventas.set_index('producto')\n",
    "precios_idx = precios.set_index('producto')\n",
    "\n",
    "ventas_idx.join(precios_idx, how='left')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 6Ô∏è‚É£ Many-to-Many\n",
    "Ejemplo con categor√≠as m√∫ltiples por producto:"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "categorias = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'producto': ['A','A','B','C','C','C'],\n",
    "    'categoria': ['x','y','x','x','y','z']\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "ventas.merge(categorias, on='producto')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 7Ô∏è‚É£ Joins temporales ‚Äî `merge_asof`\n",
    "\n",
    "Perfecto para series temporales donde quieres unir por *proximidad*."
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ts1 = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'fecha': pd.date_range('2024-01-01', periods=5),\n",
    "    'valor': [10,20,30,40,50]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "ts2 = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'fecha': pd.date_range('2024-01-01', periods=5, freq='2D'),\n",
    "    'precio': [5, 6, 7]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "pd.merge_asof(ts1, ts2, on='fecha')"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 8Ô∏è‚É£ Ejercicio pr√°ctico\n",
    "\n",
    "Usando `ventas` y `precios`:\n",
    "\n",
    "### üß© Objetivos\n",
    "1. Realiza un **left join** para a√±adir precios a ventas\n",
    "2. Calcula una columna `total = unidades * precio`\n",
    "3. Haz un **inner join** y observa qu√© productos desaparecen\n",
    "4. Crea una tabla `info` con columnas renombradas (`item`, `valor`) y haz el merge correcto\n",
    "5. Haz un merge many-to-many usando la tabla `categorias`\n",
    "\n",
    "Escribe tu soluci√≥n abajo:"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Tu soluci√≥n aqu√≠\n"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## ‚úÖ Soluci√≥n (oculta)\n",
    "<details>\n",
    "<summary>Mostrar soluciones</summary>\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "left = ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='left')\n",
    "```\n",
    "```python\n",
    "left['total'] = left['unidades'] * left['precio']\n",
    "```\n",
    "```python\n",
    "inner = ventas.merge(precios, on='producto', how='inner')\n",
    "```\n",
    "```python\n",
    "info = precios.rename(columns={'producto':'item','precio':'valor'})\n",
    "ventas.merge(info, left_on='producto', right_on='item')\n",
    "```\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ventas.merge(categorias, on='producto')\n",
    "```\n",
    "</details>"
   ]
  }
